comments: Reid (MIN) makes marginal contact to the arm of Williamson (NOP) during his shooting motion that does not affect his his ability to finish at the rim.
Hernangomez (NOP) dislodges Russell (MIN) from his legal screening position.
Hernangomez (NOP) veers into the path of Towns (MIN) and makes contact to his body as he gathers and enters his shooting motion during the driving shot attempt.
Reid (MIN) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Bledsoe (NOP) during his finish at the rim.
Ingram (NOP) legally contest the play at rim as he absorbs the contact from Russell (MIN) to the front of his body.
Russell (MIN) releases the ball, and it does not make contact with the rim or a defender before he regains possession of the ball again.
Towns (MIN) makes marginal contact to the body of Williamson (NOP) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Edwards (MIN) jumps in the air and lands back on the ground with possession of the basketball, without any contact being made to the ball from the defender.
Reid (MIN) makes contact to the arm of Williamson (NOP) during his finish at the rim.
Russell (MIN) commits a take foul on Ball (NOP).
Edwards (MIN) commits a take foul on Ball (NOP).
Vanderbilt (MIN) commits a take foul on Ingram (NOP).
Rubio (MIN) commits a take foul on Ball (NOP).
